-- Hudson City CEO Ronald Hermance passes away
-- By Amrutha Gayathri in Bangalore
-- Fri Sep 12, 2014 11:41AM EDT
-- None



Sept 12 (Reuters) - Hudson City Bancorp Inc <HCBK.O> said its Chief Executive Ronald Hermance Jr. passed away unexpectedly on Thursday evening.

Hermance, whose career spanned 26 years at Hudson City, was credited with overseeing Hudson City Savings Bank's reorganization to a publicly-held company from a mutual savings bank. [ID:nPnchbwCb] Hudson City did not say what caused Hermance's death.